  "id": "e3ed0ec97fb445d9913fc56ec42ae66b",
  "title": "Options Constructor",
  "description": "Options Constructor is the set of widget blueprints and single actor component which will help you add desired settings to your game.",
  "longDescription": "<p>The idea behind Options Constructor is to make settings windows modular and customizabable. You aren&#39;t forced to use whole premade settings window, instead you can drag&amp;drop only these parts you need.</p><p>All widget parts used to construct your own settings window can be easily customized. Just make a copy of the desired widget and change its visual part and it is ready!</p><p><br /></p><p>Features:</p><ul><li>game-ready options system</li><li>fully blueprinted</li><li>single manager component</li><li>premade widgets</li><li>keymapping system</li><li>automatically saved and loaded</li><li>stored locally</li><li>demo widget with many options implemented</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Available widgets:</p><ul><li>checkbox (boolean-based)</li><li>combobox (string-based)</li><li>cyclebox (string-based)</li><li>slider (float-based)</li><li>keymapping widget</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Documentation: <a href=\"https://t-games.pl/oc\" rel=\"nofollow\">LINK</a></p><p>Demo video: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/h8O_Edbn4-A\" rel=\"nofollow\">LINK</a></p><p>Forum thread: <a href=\"https://forums.unrealengine.com/unreal-engine/marketplace/1461720-options-constructor\" rel=\"nofollow\">LINK</a></p><p>Discord: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/YEYhpd9\" rel=\"nofollow\">LINK</a></p>",
  "technicalDetails": "<p>Number of Blueprints::</p><ul><li>4 blueprints (&#43;2 demo blueprints)</li><li>6 widget blueprints (&#43;1 demo blueprint)</li><li>several enums, structures and data tables</li><li>6 sound classes</li></ul><p>Input: Mouse</p><p>Supported Development Platforms: All</p><p>Supported Target Build Platforms: All.</p>",
